Class SystemObjectSetService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openidm.provisioner.impl.SystemObjectSetService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.forgerock.json.resource.SingletonResourceProvider, ScheduledService

    public class SystemObjectSetService
extends Object
implements ScheduledService, org.forgerock.json.resource.SingletonResourceProvider
    SystemObjectSetService is a SingletonResourceProvider to manage provisioner/connector configuration and to dispatch liveSync to the correct provisioner implementation.
